borax/borak
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:banter, ridicule
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See: also poke the borax
Pronunciation:
Notes: (The 1905 cit. has spg <i>borah,</i> which is taken as a typographical error for<i> borak</i>, which itself is less common in NZ than the folk re-formation borax)
